{
  "stem": "8895.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He thought that she was my mother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He, he, he said to her her name.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And oh, the poems.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "You'll see how much he suffered when you read his poems.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had no news whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't, I don't-- I said to my husband, did we know when the war was finished?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I can't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We would have been ecstatic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But he said, yes, we did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I can't remember it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I can't remember it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, we would have been berserk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I can't remember it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then they prepared in Russia a certain group of people of different nationalities.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They fed them very well for a while.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They dressed them better.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We had terrible things to dress.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I'll tell you about the garments we had on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And all of the sudden, we are released into freedom.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And at the last minute, they took our names with-- on, on material, written on material.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the names came up in the in America and in the news [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And it said that internment camps are dissolved.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we were still there, most of us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then the knew from every, every name and every person where we were.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It, it was good.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Russia, six years-- always a prisoner, always a prisoner.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, the garments we got-- twice a year, we got garments-- winter garments and summer garments.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a certain date, no matter how the weather was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was all clothing from dead soldiers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You could see sometimes holes from gunshots.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was always dried blood somewhere in it, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when we went-- once a week, we went for the bath.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The bath consisted of a room with boards.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
